  "2390480": {
    "name": "Beach Invasion 1945 - Pacific",
    "steam_appid": 2390480,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390480/extras/2dc7e7cbf2147ddf6f1c8d86110efaaa.poster.avif?t=1768739591\" width=620 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390480/extras/2dc7e7cbf2147ddf6f1c8d86110efaaa.webm?t=1768739591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390480/extras/2dc7e7cbf2147ddf6f1c8d86110efaaa.mp4?t=1768739591\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> Beach Invasion 1945-Pacific 是一款二战第一人称射击游戏，玩家要保卫太平洋岛屿海滩，抵御军队、坦克和飞机的入侵。 使用二战时期美国和日本帝国的各种标志性真实武器，包括机枪、舰炮和高射炮。 用地雷、炸药桶、火炮和武器升级来强化你的防御！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390480/extras/a1560d67bc4e971b24af10f50b664c0a.poster.avif?t=1768739591\" width=628 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390480/extras/a1560d67bc4e971b24af10f50b664c0a.webm?t=1768739591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390480/extras/a1560d67bc4e971b24af10f50b664c0a.mp4?t=1768739591\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> 《海滩入侵 1945-太平洋》是《海滩入侵 1944》的续作，还首次添加了与朋友一起玩多人合作游戏的选项。 玩家扮演美国或日本士兵，操纵机枪和炮塔来保护太平洋的热带岛屿。 在这些大规模的两栖和空降行动中，玩家的任务是在多挺机枪、高射炮、海军炮巢和空投补给的帮助下消灭尽可能多的入侵部队。 <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390480/extras/40f86fc06bca095e137d90e42232a998.poster.avif?t=1768739591\" width=628 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390480/extras/40f86fc06bca095e137d90e42232a998.webm?t=1768739591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390480/extras/40f86fc06bca095e137d90e42232a998.mp4?t=1768739591\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> 从两个派系和两张地图中进行选择（未来可能会有更多）：压倒日本在硫磺岛火山岛上的防御，或压倒美国在菲律宾马尼拉湾的防御。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390480/extras/acad620804ef010b810879a72501c234.poster.avif?t=1768739591\" width=628 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390480/extras/acad620804ef010b810879a72501c234.webm?t=1768739591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390480/extras/acad620804ef010b810879a72501c234.mp4?t=1768739591\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> 身临其境的二战环境中的硬核动作，具有逼真的声音和特效。 重温您最喜欢的二战电影和电视剧中难忘的史诗时刻。 在日夜变化的天气条件下不间断地进行海上和空中攻击<br>将会出现各种各样的敌人，包括海军陆战队、伞兵、火焰喷射器、火箭发射器、军舰、运输机、坦克、两栖车辆、战斗机、轰炸机等等。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390480/extras/5ccf2af25d3720d8f70a33834e7912dd.poster.avif?t=1768739591\" width=628 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390480/extras/5ccf2af25d3720d8f70a33834e7912dd.webm?t=1768739591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390480/extras/5ccf2af25d3720d8f70a33834e7912dd.mp4?t=1768739591\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> 你可以对敌人发动迫击炮攻击和雨点毁灭！<br> 获得武器的临时升级，包括毒气、穿甲弹、炸药和燃烧弹。 结合起来，它们创造了更强大的升级<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390480/extras/7cedbdcb67d21fe899b8968039d25819.poster.avif?t=1768739591\" width=628 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390480/extras/7cedbdcb67d21fe899b8968039d25819.webm?t=1768739591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390480/extras/7cedbdcb67d21fe899b8968039d25819.mp4?t=1768739591\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> 用杀伤人员地雷、反坦克地雷和爆炸性枪管强化你的防御。<br> 随着你的进步，你可以通过完成各种行动来赢得奖牌。",
